<div class=3D"ul">
<ul>
<li><span class=3D"justi">entity relationship modelling;</span></li>
<li><span class=3D"justi">class modelling;</span></li>
<li><span class=3D"justi">the relational model of data;</span></li>
<li><span class=3D"justi">the SQL database language.</span></li>
</ul>
</div>
<p class=3D"paraNoIndent1">These are not =E2=80=98exact=E2=80=99 equivalenc=
